{"prompt": "Build an e-commerce site for a bespoke leather goods store. The site should feel authentic, with an earthy yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Artisan Leather Goods</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f5e6cc; /* Earthy yellow */\n            color: #332a20; /* Dark brown for text */\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #d4a017; /* Darker earthy yellow for header */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            background-color: #e0c077; /* Lighter earthy yellow for nav */\n        }\n        nav a {\n            margin: 0 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: #332a20;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            padding: 50px 20px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4a017 0%, #f5e6cc 100%);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .products {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n        .product-card {\n            border: 1px solid #e0c077;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .product-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        .product-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 250px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n        }\n        .product-info {\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        .product-info h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            color: #d4a017;\n        }\n        .product-info p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .product-info .price {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            color: #332a20;\n        }\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #d4a017;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        .btn:hover {\n            background-color: #332a20;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            background-color: #332a20;\n            color: #f5e6cc;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                margin: 20px;\n                padding: 15px;\n            }\n            .hero h2 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n            nav a {\n                display: block;\n                margin: 10px 0;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Artisan Leather Goods</h1>\n    </header>\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n        <a href=\"#products\">Products</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"hero\">\n            <h2>Crafted with Passion, Built to Last</h2>\n            <p>Discover our collection of handcrafted leather goods, meticulously made from the finest full-grain leather. Each piece tells a story of tradition and quality.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"products\">\n            <h2>Our Signature Collection</h2>\n            <div class=\"products\">\n                <div class=\"product-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/e0c077/332a20?text=Leather+Tote\" alt=\"Leather Tote Bag\">\n                    <div class=\"product-info\">\n                        <h3>Classic Leather Tote</h3>\n                        <p>Spacious and durable, perfect for everyday use. Features a comfortable shoulder strap and internal pockets.</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$250.00</p>\n                        <button class=\"btn\">Add to Cart</button>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/d4a017/ffffff?text=Leather+Wallet\" alt=\"Leather Bifold Wallet\">\n                    <div class=\"product-info\">\n                        <h3>Bifold Leather Wallet</h3>\n                        <p>Slim and sophisticated, designed to hold your essentials with elegance. Made from rich, vegetable-tanned leather.</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$95.00</p>\n                        <button class=\"btn\">Add to Cart</button>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/e0c077/332a20?text=Leather+Journal\" alt=\"Leather Journal Cover\">\n                    <div class=\"product-info\">\n                        <h3>Handcrafted Journal Cover</h3>\n                        <p>Protect your thoughts and ideas in style. Fits a standard A5 notebook and develops a beautiful patina over time.</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$120.00</p>\n                        <button class=\"btn\">Add to Cart</button>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/d4a017/ffffff?text=Leather+Belt\" alt=\"Leather Belt\">\n                    <div class=\"product-info\">\n                        <h3>Artisan Leather Belt</h3>\n                        <p>A timeless accessory crafted from solid leather, designed to complement any outfit. Solid brass buckle.</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$110.00</p>\n                        <button class=\"btn\">Add to Cart</button>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\" style=\"margin-top: 50px; padding-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #e0c077;\">\n            <h2 style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;\">Our Story</h2>\n            <p style=\"line-height: 1.7; text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n                At Artisan Leather Goods, we believe in the enduring beauty of handcrafted items. Our journey began with a deep appreciation for traditional leatherworking techniques and a desire to create pieces that are not just functional, but also works of art. Each item is carefully cut, stitched, and finished by hand, using only the highest quality full-grain leathers. We embrace the natural variations in the leather, ensuring that no two pieces are exactly alike. Our commitment is to provide you with timeless leather goods that will accompany you for years to come, growing more beautiful with every use.\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" style=\"margin-top: 50px; text-align: center; padding: 30px; background-color: #e0c077; border-radius: 8px;\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Have questions or a custom order in mind? We'd love to hear from you.</p>\n            <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@artisanleather.com\" style=\"color: #332a20; font-weight: bold;\">info@artisanleather.com</a></p>\n            <p>Phone: <a href=\"tel:+1234567890\" style=\"color: #332a20; font-weight: bold;\">(123) 456-7890</a></p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Artisan Leather Goods. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}